menu.search_string: Kumi ʻi he Kasm ki he
menu.link_string: Fakaava ʻa e fehokotakiʻanga ʻi Kasm

text.header1: Fakaava ʻa e ngaahi fehokotakiʻanga ʻoku malu mo ʻikai ʻiloʻi ʻo fakaʻaongaʻi ʻa e Kasm-Isolation.
text.header2: ʻOku ʻomi ʻe he Kasm fakaava ʻi he browser ʻa e ngaahi meʻa ke fili mei ai ʻi he menu ke fakaava ʻa e ngaahi fehokotakiʻanga Uepi ʻi ha Workspaces browser. ʻOku ʻai ʻe he meʻa ni ke faingofua mo seamless ke fakaava ʻa e huʻuhuʻu/ʻikai ke malu URLs pe tauhi hoʻo totonu fakafoʻituitui. Koeʻuhi ʻoku fakahoko ʻa e ʻasi ʻi loto ʻi he browser workspace mamaʻo, kae ʻikai tamateʻi ʻi hoʻo komipiuta fakalotofonua, ʻoku ke lava ʻo fengaueʻaki lelei mo fakapulipuli mo e ʻasi.
text.header3: Vakai ki he fakamatala fakapepa Kasm ki ha toe ngaahi fakaikiiki.
text.form2: Fakaʻaongaʻi ʻa e ki kuo li

title.tooltip1: ʻE fakaava ʻe he ʻalu ʻa e URL ʻi ha Workspace foʻou, ko e founga mahuʻinga kuo li ki ha lele workspace
title.tooltip2: ʻI he taimi ʻoku fakaava ai ʻa e fakamatala ʻi ha fakatahaʻanga Kasm Workspaces tuku kehe kapau ko e afo ko ha URL ʻoku kei ʻaonga, ʻe ʻoatu ia ki ha misini kumi
title.tooltip3: Kapau ʻe fakaava ʻa e fakamatala ʻi ha Workspace mahalo te ke fie maʻu ke fetongi ʻa e ngaahi meʻalea ki he Workspace (kumi ʻa e tuʻunga moʻui RegExp mo delimiters/regexp/g)
